    dc:date "2016-09-28"^^xsd:string ;
    rdfs:comment """ES (PMID:11580895): Transgenic animals carrying this fusion gene expressed GFP in the bilateral AFD neurons as well as in the nine pharyngeal marginal cells (Figure 3A). The TTX-1-GFP-tagged pro-
tein is localized to the nuclei of all cells."""^^xsd:string ;
    owl:annotatedProperty ns1:BFO_0000066 ;
    owl:annotatedSource <http://model.geneontology.org/57ea2dae00000114/57ea2dae00000119> ;
